Author: Cant_get_outta_bed
Text: I second this, if nothing else stay hydrated. Pedialyte is great for electrolytes. ♥️

Author: bir_die
Text: Get some electrolytes in you! Or even see if there’s a super low calorie protein shake you can find. And use a machine that won’t eat you if you pass out and fall!!! Be safe!!!!! 💕💕💕  But also, have 100% been there yeehaw
